      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "fontSize": 14,
      "fontFamily": 1,
      "text": "1. User Request → Cognition Kernel receives task\n2. Kernel routes to Planner → Decomposes into subtasks\n3. Planner returns plan → Kernel validates each step with Validator\n4. Validator approves → Kernel checks Oversight for safety clearance\n5. Oversight approves → Kernel executes validated plan\n6. Execution completes → Explainability generates reasoning & audit trail\n7. Result returned → Full context logged via Kernel\n\nAll agents communicate ONLY through Kernel - no direct agent-to-agent calls!",
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "1. User Request → Cognition Kernel receives task\n2. Kernel routes to Planner → Decomposes into subtasks\n3. Planner returns plan → Kernel validates each step with Validator\n4. Validator approves → Kernel checks Oversight for safety clearance\n5. Oversight approves → Kernel executes validated plan\n6. Execution completes → Explainability generates reasoning & audit trail\n7. Result returned → Full context logged via Kernel\n\nAll agents communicate ONLY through Kernel - no direct agent-to-agent calls!",
      "lineHeight": 1.25,
      "baseline": 119
    }
  ],
